here are the latest, unofficial results in the democratic presidential primary in connecticut on tuesday
739 of 739 precincts reporting - 100 percent
dukakis, 139,968 - 58 percent
gephardt, 1,018 - 0 percent
gore, 18,542 - 8 percent
jackson, 68,193 - 28 percent
