what we are paying her is the equivalent of an advanced associate professor's salary or a beginning salary for a tenured professor. with her life experiences and credentials, we believe she's a bargain at this price,'' said edward azar, head of the university's center for international development and conflict management
he said mrs. sadat's salary comes from the university of maryland foundation, which receives donations for research
